   <dc:title>Handwritten lettercard from Moriz Schenker to Jeanette Schenker, dated September 16,
    1930</dc:title>

   <dcterms:created>1930-09-12T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
   <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2024-02-19</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
   <dc:description>Moriz Schenker reassures Jeanette that things are going ahead [on mortgage for
    the Arzberg property and return of Heinrich's investment], hopes that Heinrich's health is
    improving, and conveys the pressure under which he is working.</dc:description>
   <dc:subject/>
  </sdo:itemDesc>


